                <p><lb/><g type="cross">+</g> Ἡ <supplied reason="omitted">ε</supplied>ἰρήνη τοῦ σωτῆρος ἡμὼν <expan><abbr>Χ</abbr><ex>ριστο</ex><abbr>ῦ</abbr></expan>
