                    <lb/>φυλάξῃ πάσῃ σοφίᾳ πνεύματος
                    <lb/>καὶ ἐν πίστι τῶν πρώτων Ἁγίων τὰς <supplied reason="omitted">ε</supplied>ἰσόδους
                    <lb/>καὶ τὰς ἐξόδους ὑμῶν ἐν Κυρίῳ
                    <lb/><g type="cross">+</g> Ἀμήν <g type="cross">+</g></p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>… Let your coming be in peace, your staying of a long time be governed by the
                    grace of God. Amen.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ends with a  quotations of Ps. 122:8.</p>
